            MENU = deterministic option always shown if eligible. POOL = NPC draws from a pool per visit (mission-style; #686).

            * `menu` - Menu
            * `pool` - Pool
        eligibility_rule:
          description: Predicate JSON evaluated via `world.missions.predicates.evaluate`.
